{
  "video_id": "6oLsJUH1cfU",
  "title": "Medical tech designed to meet Africa's needs | Soyapi Mumba",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12760.0,
      "end_time": 16216.0,
      "text": "Like every passionate software engineer out there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16239.0,
      "end_time": 19575.0,
      "text": "I closely follow technology companies in Silicon Valley,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19600.0,
      "end_time": 22720.0,
      "text": "pretty much the same way soccer fans follow their teams in Europe."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 23640.0,
      "end_time": 25856.0,
      "text": "I read articles on tech blogs"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 25880.0,
      "end_time": 28000.0,
      "text": "and listen to podcasts on my phone."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 29800.0,
      "end_time": 30895.0,
      "text": "But after I finish the article,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 30920.0,
      "end_time": 34256.0,
      "text": "lock my phone and unplug the headphones,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 34280.0,
      "end_time": 36496.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m back in sub-Saharan Africa,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 36520.0,
      "end_time": 38960.0,
      "text": "where the landscape is not quite the same."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 40160.0,
      "end_time": 42800.0,
      "text": "We have long and frequent power outages,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 43720.0,
      "end_time": 45775.0,
      "text": "low penetration of computers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 45800.0,
      "end_time": 47736.0,
      "text": "slow internet connections"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 47760.0,
      "end_time": 52160.0,
      "text": "and a lot of patients visiting understaffed hospitals."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 52400.0,
      "end_time": 54176.0,
      "text": "Since the HIV epidemic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 54200.0,
      "end_time": 59856.0,
      "text": "hospitals have been struggling to manage regular HIV treatment records"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 59880.0,
      "end_time": 61720.0,
      "text": "for increasing volumes of patients."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 62720.0,
      "end_time": 64456.0,
      "text": "For such environments,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 64480.00000000001,
      "end_time": 68376.0,
      "text": "importing technology systems developed elsewhere has not worked,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 68400.0,
      "end_time": 71616.0,
      "text": "but in 2006, I joined Baobab Health,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 71640.0,
      "end_time": 75176.0,
      "text": "a team that uses locally based engineers"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 75200.0,
      "end_time": 77816.0,
      "text": "to develop suitable interventions"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 77840.0,
      "end_time": 81696.0,
      "text": "that are addressing health care challenges in Malawi."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 81720.0,
      "end_time": 85136.0,
      "text": "We designed an electronic health record system"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 85160.0,
      "end_time": 88496.0,
      "text": "that is used by health care workers while seeing patients."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 88520.0,
      "end_time": 93950.0,
      "text": "And in the process we realized that we not only had to design the software,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 93120.0,
      "end_time": 95480.0,
      "text": "we had to implement the infrastructure as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 96640.0,
      "end_time": 98856.0,
      "text": "We don&#39;t have enough medical staff"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 98880.0,
      "end_time": 101735.0,
      "text": "to comprehensively examine every patient,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 101760.0,
      "end_time": 104816.0,
      "text": "so we embedded clinical guidelines within the software"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 104840.0,
      "end_time": 107160.0,
      "text": "to guide nurses and clerks"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 107400.0,
      "end_time": 109200.0,
      "text": "who assist with handling some of the workload."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 110000.0,
      "end_time": 111656.0,
      "text": "Everyone has a birthday,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 111680.0,
      "end_time": 114176.0,
      "text": "but not everyone knows their birthday,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 114200.0,
      "end_time": 118160.0,
      "text": "so we wrote algorithms to handle estimated birthdates"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 118400.0,
      "end_time": 119320.0,
      "text": "as complete dates."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 120200.0,
      "end_time": 124136.0,
      "text": "How do we follow up patients living in slums"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 124160.0,
      "end_time": 126360.0,
      "text": "with no street and house numbers?"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 127200.0,
      "end_time": 131800.0,
      "text": "We used landmarks to approximate their physical addresses."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 132400.0,
      "end_time": 135480.0,
      "text": "Malawi had no IDs to uniquely identify patients,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 136480.0,
      "end_time": 139616.0,
      "text": "so we had to implement unique patient IDs"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 139640.0,
      "end_time": 141880.0,
      "text": "to link patient records across clinics."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 142919.0,
      "end_time": 145360.0,
      "text": "The IDs are printed as barcodes"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 146200.0,
      "end_time": 149550.0,
      "text": "on labels that are stuck on personal health booklets"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 149800.0,
      "end_time": 150280.0,
      "text": "kept by each patient."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 151000.0,
      "end_time": 152976.0,
      "text": "With this barcoded ID,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 153000.0,
      "end_time": 155416.0,
      "text": "a simple scan with a barcode reader"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 155440.0,
      "end_time": 157680.0,
      "text": "quickly pulls up the patient&#39;s records."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 158440.0,
      "end_time": 160736.0,
      "text": "No need to rewrite their personal details"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 160760.0,
      "end_time": 163176.0,
      "text": "on paper registers at every visit."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 163200.0,
      "end_time": 165856.0,
      "text": "And suddenly, queues became shorter."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 165880.0,
      "end_time": 170775.0,
      "text": "This meant patients, typically mothers with little children on their backs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 170800.0,
      "end_time": 173936.0,
      "text": "had to spend less time waiting to be assisted."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 173960.0,
      "end_time": 175896.0,
      "text": "And if they lose their booklets,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 175920.0,
      "end_time": 179950.0,
      "text": "their records can still be pulled by searching with their names."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 179120.0,
      "end_time": 183840.0,
      "text": "Now, the way we pronounce and spell names varies tremendously."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 184360.0,
      "end_time": 186640.0,
      "text": "We freely mix R&#39;s and L&#39;s,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 187800.0,
      "end_time": 189920.0,
      "text": "English and vernacular versions of their names."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 190680.0,
      "end_time": 192960.0,
      "text": "Even soundex,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 192120.0,
      "end_time": 196536.0,
      "text": "a standard method for grouping words by how similar they sound,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 196560.0,
      "end_time": 198136.0,
      "text": "was not good enough."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 198160.0,
      "end_time": 199856.0,
      "text": "So we had to modify it"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 199880.0,
      "end_time": 203680.0,
      "text": "to help us link and match existing records."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 206160.0,
      "end_time": 207359.0,
      "text": "Before the iPhone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 208400.0,
      "end_time": 211856.0,
      "text": "software engineers developed for personal computers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 211880.0,
      "end_time": 213136.0,
      "text": "but from our experience,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 213160.0,
      "end_time": 216536.0,
      "text": "we knew our power system is not reliable enough"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 216560.0,
      "end_time": 217840.0,
      "text": "for personal computers."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 218480.0,
      "end_time": 223136.0,
      "text": "So we repurposed touch screen point-of-sale terminals"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 223160.0,
      "end_time": 224856.0,
      "text": "that are meant for retail shops"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 224880.0,
      "end_time": 226640.0,
      "text": "to become clinical workstations."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 227920.0,
      "end_time": 232790.0,
      "text": "At the time, we imported internet appliances called i-Openers"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 232960.0,
      "end_time": 235976.0,
      "text": "that were manufactured during the dot-com era"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 236000.0,
      "end_time": 237840.0,
      "text": "by a failed US company."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 239800.0,
      "end_time": 241376.0,
      "text": "We modified their screens"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 241400.0,
      "end_time": 242776.0,
      "text": "to add touch sensors"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 242800.0,
      "end_time": 246120.0,
      "text": "and their power system to run from rechargeable batteries."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 246680.0,
      "end_time": 251816.0,
      "text": "When we started, we didn&#39;t find a reliable network to transmit data,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 251840.0,
      "end_time": 253480.0,
      "text": "especially from rural hospitals."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 254240.0,
      "end_time": 256960.0,
      "text": "So we built our own towers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 257720.00000000003,
      "end_time": 259616.00000000003,
      "text": "created a wireless network"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 259640.0,
      "end_time": 262550.0,
      "text": "and linked clinics in Lilongwe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 262790.0,
      "end_time": 263280.0,
      "text": "Malawi&#39;s capital."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 264600.0,
      "end_time": 267480.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 269600.0,
      "end_time": 271200.0,
      "text": "With a team of engineers"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 272200.0,
      "end_time": 274496.0,
      "text": "working within a hospital campus,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 274520.0,
      "end_time": 277176.0,
      "text": "we observed health care workers use the system"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 277200.0,
      "end_time": 280416.0,
      "text": "and iteratively build an information system"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 280440.0,
      "end_time": 284256.0,
      "text": "that is now managing HIV records"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 284280.0,
      "end_time": 287895.0,
      "text": "in all major public hospitals in Malawi."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 287920.0,
      "end_time": 293120.0,
      "text": "These are hospitals serving over 2,000 HIV patients, each clinic."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 294680.0,
      "end_time": 297536.0,
      "text": "Now, health care workers who used to spend days"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 297560.0,
      "end_time": 299696.0,
      "text": "to tally and prepare quarterly reports"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 299720.0,
      "end_time": 301960.0,
      "text": "are producing the same reports within minutes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 302960.0,
      "end_time": 306816.0,
      "text": "and health care experts from all over the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 306840.0,
      "end_time": 309880.0,
      "text": "are now coming to Malawi to learn how we did it."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 310880.0,
      "end_time": 314336.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 314360.0,
      "end_time": 316936.0,
      "text": "It is inspiring and fun"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 316960.0,
      "end_time": 319775.0,
      "text": "to follow technology trends across the globe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 319800.0,
      "end_time": 321896.0,
      "text": "but to make them work"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 321920.0,
      "end_time": 324960.0,
      "text": "in low-resourced environments"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 324120.0,
      "end_time": 327296.0,
      "text": "like public hospitals in sub-Saharan Africa,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 327320.0,
      "end_time": 331960.0,
      "text": "we have had to become jacks-of-all-trades"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 331120.0,
      "end_time": 334656.0,
      "text": "and build whole systems, including the infrastructure,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 334680.0,
      "end_time": 335920.0,
      "text": "from the ground up."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 336560.0,
      "end_time": 337776.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 337800.0,
      "end_time": 342800.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}